":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T07:20:54.000Z","msg":"最好睇個集應該 屌柒寶蓮寺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4b9786117988f2da3b30d566386ceb6012ccdca","tid":634314,"uid":112241,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T07:22:25.000Z","msg":"其實我好懷疑佢識唔識食野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你地睇佢的片，所有！係所有食物擺入口，三秒內一定吞撚左落肚，我肯撚定佢連食緊咩都唔知。"},{"pid":"3fb8efbf7f9dc1642185b776e3c12008287ff1eb","tid":634314,"uid":33868,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T07:23:03.000Z","msg":"不過維記潤牛面真係屌得好"},{"pid":"8ffe711fae4a32065f71b9fd3652b341902cb560","tid":634314,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T07:23:45.000Z","msg":"有 但聽講佢地屌客？"},{"pid":"cad02266202cc1b7968633add5f14b1f1465e101","tid":634314,"uid":97290,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T07:23:52.000Z","msg":"睇得多會搞到個人都好燥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d68798fdd8372fb74fbdc8eacd6226de58734585","tid":634314,"uid":33721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T07:24:01.000Z","msg":"d粗口有d為講而講  但內容ok 有時睇佢屌人幾過癮"},{"pid":"d35cc40b909b30081afc635782e46f477f5cf04a","tid":634314,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T07:25:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"26d3223bbf254e4a1f13bf23b33bd34612e7344b","tid":634314,"uid":88029,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T07:32:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"11cd5c502f2484011a70c994b8b0f4b53b3816be","tid":634314,"uid":11148,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"26d3223bbf254e4a1f13bf23b33bd34612e7344b","tid":634314,"uid":88029,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e0051bdca838bd5dadc7a700cac21f4a2282161","tid":634314,"uid":4145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13bc8396d75d622146f74c35f1cbb0291c02b27a","tid":634314,"uid":88029,"like":0,"dislike":3,"sco